{"tid":1125251,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"#同我出力打 馮盈盈怪叫聲迴盪健身室","createTime":"2019-04-25T14:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T06:06:39.000Z","uid":54870,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dbf54849983fb9416d576cf1db97d143a536c99a","tid":1125251,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T14:33:53.000Z","msg":"馮盈盈言論一向大膽，不少金句都挑戰女士底線，之前為《美女廚房》宣傳，更自拍伸脷食香蕉相，大玩性暗示。今日馮盈盈就在IG story上載一條健身片，又留tag「#同我出力打」、「#睇落好似好輕力」、「#痛到個肚紅曬」，健身同時教練又用圓柱型大碌棍拍打馮盈盈，每打一次馮盈盈都未打先驚，不斷發出「呀~」的叫聲，聽得人心癢癢。"},{"pid":"9ba2716fb38fdb50fc4696e27213fc675002fe61","tid":1125251,"uid":54870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T14:35:33.000Z","msg":"AppleDaily:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190425/59529563\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190425%2F59529563&d=fAF%2FER2cs4qp%2F6NYk0BreANVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=5a162d73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190425%2F59529563&h=4a5732d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190425/59529563</a><br />\n<br />\n冇登記蘋果:<a href=\"https://vimeo.com/332458173\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvimeo.com%2F332458173&d=fAF%2FER2cs4qp%2F6NYk0BreANVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=1b46d90d\" target=\"_blank\">https://vimeo.com/332458173</a>"},{"pid":"6099eaf51bb69463dd8ff5f0e2007c6d89a4fe0b","tid":1125251,"uid":118827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T14:36:01.000Z","msg":"往死裡打thanks"},{"pid":"426be48df08578dc4629f08ac1d0b116d63d2624","tid":1125251,"uid":54870,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T14:51:21.000Z","msg":"補番3張gif先<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bjGAgZJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbj